#: _posts/2023-02-15-quarkus-3-0-0-alpha4-released.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Quarkus 3.0.0.Alpha4 released - Fourth iteration of our Jakarta EE 10 stream"
msgstr "Quarkus 3.0.0.Alpha4发布 - 我们的Jakarta EE 10流的第四次迭代"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#: _posts/2023-02-15-quarkus-3-0-0-alpha4-released.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"This version marks a huge milestone: the Jakarta EE 10 work has been "
"integrated into our main branch."
msgstr "这个版本标志着一个巨大的里程碑：Jakarta EE 10的工作已经被整合到我们的主分支中。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2023-02-15-quarkus-3-0-0-alpha4-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"As you might know by now, we started a Quarkus 3.0 effort last year and we "
"are continuing this effort, which was described https://quarkus.io/blog/road-"
"to-quarkus-3/[here], https://quarkus.io/blog/our-bumpy-road-to-jakarta-ee-10/"
"[here], https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-0-0-alpha1-released/[here], and "
"https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-0-0-alpha3-released/[here]."
msgstr ""
"正如你现在可能知道的，我们去年开始了Quarkus 3.0的努力，我们正在继续这一努力， link:https://quarkus.io/blog/"
"road-to-quarkus-3/[这里] 、 link:https://quarkus.io/blog/our-bumpy-road-to-"
"jakarta-ee-10/[这里] 、 link:https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-0-0-alpha1-"
"released/[这里] 和 link:https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-0-0-alpha3-released/"
"[这里] 都有描述。"

#: _posts/2023-02-15-quarkus-3-0-0-alpha4-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus 3.0.0.Alpha4 is the fourth iteration of this work and it marks a "
"huge milestone:\n"
"the Jakarta EE 10 stream is now our default stream as the Jakarta EE 10 work "
"has been integrated in the `main` branch of the Quarkus repository."
msgstr ""
"Quarkus 3.0.0.Alpha4 是这项工作的第四次迭代，它标志着一个巨大的里程碑：Jakarta EE 10 "
"数据流现在是我们的默认数据流，因为 Jakarta EE 10 工作已集成到 Quarkus 软件库的 `main` 分支中。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2023-02-15-quarkus-3-0-0-alpha4-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"On the Jakarta EE 10 front, it comes with minor upgrades all over the place "
"to use the latest versions of the specs and implementations."
msgstr "在Jakarta EE 10方面，它到处都有小的升级，以使用最新版本的规格和实现。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2023-02-15-quarkus-3-0-0-alpha4-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But this version also comes with several new features and enhancements:"
